For operator-facing tone rules, see [`docs/CLI_TONE_RULES.md`](CLI_TONE_RULES.md).
For section ordering and output-shape rules, see [`docs/CLI_OUTPUT_ANATOMY.md`](CLI_OUTPUT_ANATOMY.md).

